extends layout

block content
  div(class="p-4 main-container")
    h1 The #{title}
    hr
    p(class="mb-2") Here you can see an overall view of the collection and its records.

    p(class="mb-3") The collection currently has the following record counts: 

    ul
      li(class="mb-1") #[strong Games:] !{game_count}
      li(class="mb-1") #[strong Developers:] !{developer_count}
      li(class="mb-1") #[strong Genres:] !{genre_count}
      li(class="mb-1") #[strong Platforms:] !{platform_count}

    p Create new games, developers and more to help these numbers grow even bigger.